OL,3,CChanging fiscal rules could enable
OL,4,C#50bn of extra borrowing for investment
OL,6,FIn theory, the rules are binding. In
OL,7,Fpractice, Chancellors sometimes revise
OL,8,Fthem when it becomes inconvenient.
OL,10,FYesterday, Rachel Reeves gave a clear
OL,11,Fsignal that she is thinking of
OL,12,Fchanging one of the fiscal rules in
OL,13,FLabour's manifesto - specifically, the
OL,14,Fpledge to get debt falling as a share
OL,15,Fof national income in five years - to
OL,16,Fincrease public investment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
