OL,3,CChanging fiscal rules could enable
OL,4,C#50bn of extra borrowing for investment
OL,6,F"It's time that the Treasury moved on
OL,7,Ffrom just counting the costs of
OL,8,Finvestments in our economy, to
OL,9,Frecognising the benefits too," she
OL,10,Ftold the conference.
OL,12,FBen Zaranko, Senior Research Economist
OL,13,Fat the Institute for Fiscal Studies,
OL,14,Fcalculates that if the chancellor
OL,15,Fdecided to move from targeting Public
OL,16,FSector Net Debt to a broader measure
OL,17,Fof the government's balance sheet,
OL,18,Flike Public Sector Net Worth, it could
OL,19,Fenable the Rachel Reeves to borrow an
OL,20,Fextra #50 billion a year for
OL,21,Finvestment, without raising taxes
