OL,3,CChanging fiscal rules could enable
OL,4,C#50bn of extra borrowing for investment
OL,6,FRaising public investment by this
OL,7,Famount and holding it there would be a
OL,8,Fradical change, doubling the scheduled
OL,9,Flevel of investment in the final year
OL,10,Fof this parliament.
OL,12,F"For a government seeking to invest
OL,13,Fmore without a need to raise taxes,
OL,14,Fthis has obvious attractions," says
OL,15,FZaranko.
OL,17,F"But it has downsides too. These
OL,18,Fmeasures are complicated, hard to
OL,19,Festimate, and not always helpful for
OL,20,Fthinking about whether the
OL,21,Fgovernment's borrowing is sustainable.
