OL,3,CChanging fiscal rules could enable
OL,4,C#50bn of extra borrowing for investment
OL,6,FAs things stand, government investment
OL,7,Fis scheduled to fall as a share of
OL,8,Fnational income over the course of
OL,9,Fthis parliament.
OL,11,FAnd the fiscal rules Labour is
OL,12,Fcurrently committed to make it
OL,13,Fdifficult to avoid these cuts.
OL,15,FSome have urged the government to
OL,16,Famend and even ditch the fiscal rules,
OL,17,Farguing there's a need for much more
OL,18,Fboldness than was set out in the
OL,19,FLabour manifesto.
